reviewText: Superb video sand worth the price for those of who are fans of Red.

This is the Greatest interview, I have ever seen.  Even if you don't know of Red Skelton, this is a great way to discover him.
  He understands his craft and can move you from Laughter to Tears and back all in the same story.
  The only bad thing about it, is in knowing that Red is no longer here, and that there is no one to replace him.
